FBIS4-61247 "drsov087_g_94005" FBIS-SOV-94-087 Daily Report 4 May 1994 WESTERN REGION Belarus Representatives of UN Drugs Control Board To Visit Representatives of UN Drugs Control Board To Visit WS0405135994 Minsk BELAPAN in Belarusian 1236 GMT 4 May 94 WS0405135994 Minsk BELAPAN Belarusian BFN [Excerpt] Between 4 and 6 May, representatives of the UN International Narcotics Control Board [INCB] will be paying an official visit to Belarus. The main goal of the visit is to discuss international treaties concerning the fight against drugs, cooperation between Belarus and the INCB, technical assistance to Belarus in this area, and the development of a national mechanism for controlling the production and distribution of drugs and psychotropic substances. It is expected that in the course of the visit, the INCB representatives will meet with Belarusian Interior Ministry leaders and workers from various Interior Ministry departments. [passage omitted]
